  m_text: "Welcome, Botanist.\r\n\r\nYour mission is to restore this abandoned greenhouse.\r\n\r\n\u2022
    Seed energy increases automatically over time.\r\n\u2022 Strike the Mother Seed
    to gain extra Seed.\r\n\u2022 Plant in empty pots to increase passive generation.\r\n\u2022
    Use Crystals to multiply plant output.\r\n\u2022 Reach 1,000 Seed to unlock the
    Crystal Chamber.\r\n\r\nPress OK to begin."
